   "source": [
    "# ToxScout AI - Tox21 Ensemble Training Pipeline\n",
    "This notebook demonstrates the end-to-end training pipeline for the ToxScout AI toxicity prediction engine.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Pipeline Overview:**\n",
    "1. **Data Loading:** Parsing 10,000+ compounds from the Tox21 dataset.\n",
    "2. **Feature Extraction:** Generating 2048-bit Morgan Fingerprints (R=2) and RDKit physicochemical descriptors (Lipinski rules).\n",
    "3. **Model Training:** Training 12 distinct soft-voting ensembles (XGBoost, Random Forest, LightGBM) for each Tox21 nuclear receptor and stress response pathway.\n",
    "4. **Evaluation:** Calculating ROC-AUC and PR-AUC with 5-fold cross-validation.\n",
    "5. **XAI Export:** Exporting SHAP TreeExplainers for frontend feature importance."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "from rdkit import Chem\n",
    "from rdkit.Chem import AllChem, Descriptors\n",
    "import xgboost as xgb\n",
    "from sklearn.ensemble import RandomForestClassifier, VotingClassifier\n",
    "from sklearn.model_selection import StratifiedKFold\n",
    "from sklearn.metrics import roc_auc_score, average_precision_score\n",
    "import shap\n",
    "import joblib"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
